WEBVTT

﻿1
00:00:07.640 --> 00:00:09.039
{\an8}[male voice] <i>I dream of you.</i>

2
00:00:09.040 --> 00:00:11.519
{\an8}[ethereal music playing]

3
00:00:11.520 --> 00:00:13.080
{\an8}[hooves drumming]

4
00:00:14.600 --> 00:00:15.800
{\an8}[horse snorts]

5
00:00:20.720 --> 00:00:21.760
