13
00:00:57.600 --> 00:00:58.959
[music fades]

14
00:00:58.960 --> 00:01:01.239
{\an8}[upbeat soul music playing]
<i>♪ In the summer of '16 ♪</i>

15
00:01:01.240 --> 00:01:03.559
{\an8}<i>♪ Was it love or nicotine ♪</i>

16
00:01:03.560 --> 00:01:08.119
{\an8}<i>♪ That made us
